00:01:24.990 --> 00:01:28.140
[Whispers of Fate]

00:01:28.380 --> 00:01:29.950
[Episode 21]

00:01:46.310 --> 00:01:47.240
What's going on?

00:01:47.380 --> 00:01:48.780
Aren't you scared at all?

00:01:49.630 --> 00:01:51.070
Lici, are you really that silly?

00:01:51.070 --> 00:01:52.870
Don't you even understand fear?

00:01:53.570 --> 00:01:55.280
Forget it. You wouldn't understand anyway.

00:01:55.280 --> 00:01:56.740
But there is a kind of sound

00:01:57.340 --> 00:01:59.940
that you can feel
even if you don't understand.

00:02:09.370 --> 00:02:10.780
What is this?

00:02:12.520 --> 00:02:13.830
Can I try too?

00:02:14.360 --> 00:02:15.560
This is called music.

00:02:18.829 --> 00:02:19.160
Here.

00:02:20.200 --> 00:02:20.600
Try it.

00:02:56.329 --> 00:02:57.790
I know what would suit you.

00:02:58.100 --> 00:02:59.760
Senior has hidden a Mindfast Fox-Dragon.

00:02:59.760 --> 00:03:00.830
I'll find it for you now.

00:03:00.830 --> 00:03:01.360
Let's go.

00:03:01.800 --> 00:03:04.080
What is the Mindfast Fox-Dragon?

00:03:04.770 --> 00:03:05.970
It's a real treasure,

00:03:06.410 --> 00:03:08.220
a flute that's very difficult to master.

00:03:08.220 --> 00:03:10.290
What's a flute?

00:03:14.450 --> 00:03:15.380
Dinner's ready.

00:03:19.850 --> 00:03:21.230
Don't growl at me, little monster.

00:03:21.230 --> 00:03:21.960
Come with me.

00:03:31.710 --> 00:03:33.170
Fang Zhou's heart crystal

00:03:34.060 --> 00:03:35.500
is now inside my body,

00:03:36.850 --> 00:03:37.690
and his body

00:03:38.840 --> 00:03:40.900
has been hidden by me in Zhoudi Tower,

00:03:41.030 --> 00:03:41.240
preserved in the Immortal Crystal Coffin

00:03:41.240 --> 00:03:42.470
[Fang Zhou's Tomb]

00:03:42.470 --> 00:03:43.600
of the Biluo Palace.

00:03:43.800 --> 00:03:45.060
His spiritual essence

00:03:45.120 --> 00:03:46.520
and vitality are intact.

00:03:47.990 --> 00:03:49.140
As long as I use the Rebirth Scroll

00:03:49.140 --> 00:03:50.190
to restore it.

00:04:05.000 --> 00:04:06.510
Tang Lici.

00:04:07.240 --> 00:04:08.560
I'm such a fool.

00:04:10.420 --> 00:04:12.700
I actually wanted to trust you again.

00:04:35.400 --> 00:04:37.360
[Zhoudi Tower]

00:04:43.480 --> 00:04:46.750
♪ Master ♪

00:04:47.320 --> 00:04:51.890
♪ You failed to take the Biluo Palace ♪

00:04:52.000 --> 00:04:56.390
♪ And couldn't kill Tang Lici ♪

00:04:57.070 --> 00:05:01.560
♪ How dare you go back to your old home? ♪

00:05:01.810 --> 00:05:03.000
You really don't take

00:05:03.000 --> 00:05:04.430
the Fengliu Shop seriously anymore.

00:05:04.430 --> 00:05:05.830
I was only gone for 2 days.

00:05:06.430 --> 00:05:08.660
Can't the Fengliu Shop stay in business
anymore?

00:05:08.660 --> 00:05:10.240
Master, since your disappearance,

00:05:10.240 --> 00:05:12.370
the Sword Alliance
has made thorough preparations.

00:05:12.370 --> 00:05:13.660
Tang Lici has become

00:05:13.690 --> 00:05:15.650
the Guest of Honor of the Sword Alliance.

00:05:15.650 --> 00:05:17.380
He didn't lose his reputation.

00:05:17.750 --> 00:05:18.950
Instead, he's become

00:05:19.310 --> 00:05:20.480
the most famous marital artist

00:05:20.480 --> 00:05:22.280
in the current martial arts world.

00:05:22.280 --> 00:05:23.950
He's significantly strengthened
the Sword Alliance,

00:05:23.950 --> 00:05:25.920
enabling it to amass sufficient fame,
fortune, and influence.

00:05:25.920 --> 00:05:26.830
He also has a group of

00:05:26.830 --> 00:05:28.430
friends willing to die protecting him.

00:05:28.430 --> 00:05:29.760
He's now second to none.

00:05:30.480 --> 00:05:31.080
But you are

00:05:31.870 --> 00:05:32.830
notorious in the martial arts world

00:05:32.830 --> 00:05:34.690
as the Master of the Fengliu Shop,

00:05:35.070 --> 00:05:36.870
bringing shame to Zhoudi Tower.

00:05:41.360 --> 00:05:42.630
Leader, do you really think

00:05:42.630 --> 00:05:44.890
Tang Lici is helping the Sword Alliance?

00:05:45.409 --> 00:05:46.270
You're sworn enemies.

00:05:46.270 --> 00:05:47.870
You can certainly see through him.

00:05:47.870 --> 00:05:48.680
His next move

00:05:48.680 --> 00:05:50.070
is already clear to you.

00:05:50.600 --> 00:05:51.480
Tang Lici is merely

00:05:51.480 --> 00:05:52.480
using these fools

00:05:52.600 --> 00:05:54.040
to deal with the Fengliu Shop.

00:05:54.040 --> 00:05:55.120
He wants them to be

00:05:55.510 --> 00:05:57.270
his pawns and scapegoats,

00:05:57.560 --> 00:05:59.000
paving his way to hell.

00:05:59.830 --> 00:06:01.750
If Tang Lici can use the Sword Alliance,

00:06:01.750 --> 00:06:03.920
you can also use me to kill him.

00:06:05.000 --> 00:06:06.800
You think I can't kill him?

00:06:07.680 --> 00:06:08.920
He is a true monster,

00:06:09.160 --> 00:06:10.560
while you're not yet one.

00:06:11.390 --> 00:06:12.720
That's why

00:06:12.720 --> 00:06:14.510
you can't kill Tang Lici.

00:06:16.190 --> 00:06:17.750
You don't do enough good
to be truly virtuous,

00:06:17.750 --> 00:06:19.750
nor can you commit great evil.

00:06:20.240 --> 00:06:20.680
Yan,

00:06:21.310 --> 00:06:22.480
with your personality,

00:06:22.480 --> 00:06:24.240
you can never reach
the extremes of good or evil.

00:06:24.240 --> 00:06:24.950
In the end,

00:06:25.430 --> 00:06:27.390
you're destined to accomplish nothing.

00:06:27.390 --> 00:06:29.720
Only I can kill Tang Lici!

00:06:30.390 --> 00:06:31.590
Whoever touches him,

00:06:32.610 --> 00:06:33.930
I will kill them.

00:06:36.990 --> 00:06:37.650
As you wish.

00:06:57.230 --> 00:06:57.790
Master.

00:06:59.070 --> 00:07:00.200
I finally found you.

00:07:00.720 --> 00:07:02.120
I'm so worried about you.

00:07:03.430 --> 00:07:04.890
Summon everyone to see me.

00:07:23.050 --> 00:07:24.380
Hidden-Wing Curse Bug.

00:07:24.630 --> 00:07:25.960
Using it as eyes and ears

00:07:26.370 --> 00:07:27.970
for searching and scouting.

00:07:29.300 --> 00:07:30.890
What is Liu Yan looking for?

00:07:32.030 --> 00:07:33.090
Why did he suddenly

00:07:33.870 --> 00:07:35.200
return to Zhoudi Tower?

00:07:36.310 --> 00:07:37.480
Why overthink it?

00:07:37.960 --> 00:07:39.270
Let's investigate this Zhoudi Tower,

00:07:39.270 --> 00:07:40.330
and we'll find out.

00:07:45.330 --> 00:07:46.530
If Liu Yan can't track things down

00:07:46.530 --> 00:07:48.330
with the Hidden-Wing Curse Bug,

00:07:48.360 --> 00:07:50.020
I can't find anything either.

00:07:50.030 --> 00:07:52.000
Of course, we need
to ask the puppetry master

00:07:52.000 --> 00:07:53.600
Qiaoyi Qiankun to investigate.

00:07:53.600 --> 00:07:54.510
He attacked the Biluo Palace

00:07:54.510 --> 00:07:56.770
by using up a Sky-Fallen Stone fragment.

00:07:57.000 --> 00:07:58.270
He can't continue his research.

00:07:58.270 --> 00:07:59.820
Now, apart from the Biluo Palace,

00:07:59.820 --> 00:08:01.880
only Puti Valley
possesses Sky-Fallen Stones.

00:08:01.880 --> 00:08:03.000
If you give him another one,

00:08:03.000 --> 00:08:04.930
he'll be eternally grateful to you

00:08:05.830 --> 00:08:07.360
and willing to do anything.

00:08:07.750 --> 00:08:08.800
You're right.

00:08:09.160 --> 00:08:11.490
I can't believe
I had to remind you of this.

00:08:11.520 --> 00:08:12.640
What a fool.

00:08:14.070 --> 00:08:14.870
You may leave.

00:08:24.030 --> 00:08:26.070
For what happened in the Qingyang Realm,

00:08:26.070 --> 00:08:27.470
thank you, Master Puzhu.

00:08:28.710 --> 00:08:30.110
I am willing to cooperate

00:08:30.310 --> 00:08:31.750
because the Sword Alliance truly

00:08:31.750 --> 00:08:32.809
needs Mr. Tang now.

00:08:33.120 --> 00:08:34.240
Yielding to circumstances

00:08:34.240 --> 00:08:35.150
doesn't mean

00:08:35.480 --> 00:08:36.549
I agree with

00:08:36.549 --> 00:08:37.679
Mr. Tang's methods.

00:08:37.850 --> 00:08:38.480
Same here.

00:08:42.030 --> 00:08:43.960
Whatever works is a good strategy.

00:08:44.250 --> 00:08:45.080
Why would I need

00:08:45.080 --> 00:08:46.000
your approval?

00:08:46.000 --> 00:08:47.630
Using money to buy loyalty

00:08:48.400 --> 00:08:49.460
is not a good start.

00:08:49.510 --> 00:08:50.710
Without any benefit,

00:08:50.840 --> 00:08:52.120
you expect those disciples

00:08:52.120 --> 00:08:53.600
to risk their lives fighting evil.

00:08:53.600 --> 00:08:54.320
Is that fair?

00:08:54.320 --> 00:08:55.370
Using profit as bait

00:08:55.370 --> 00:08:56.630
will lead to betrayal for profit.

00:08:56.630 --> 00:08:58.050
The Evil Pill spreads its poison

00:08:58.050 --> 00:08:59.770
precisely because of human greed

00:08:59.770 --> 00:09:01.700
and delusions of instant success.

00:09:05.280 --> 00:09:06.690
Pursuing benefits and avoiding harm

00:09:06.690 --> 00:09:07.900
is human nature.

00:09:08.360 --> 00:09:09.910
Isn't it a bit harsh

00:09:09.910 --> 00:09:11.240
to hold ordinary people

00:09:11.240 --> 00:09:12.480
to a sage's standard?

00:09:20.550 --> 00:09:22.200
This is what they call,
"With great rewards

00:09:22.200 --> 00:09:23.130
come brave men."

00:09:24.030 --> 00:09:25.550
After the news has gotten out,

00:09:25.550 --> 00:09:26.910
many sects want to join

00:09:26.910 --> 00:09:29.030
the Sword Alliance's campaign
against the Fengliu Shop.

00:09:29.030 --> 00:09:29.720
Moreover,

00:09:29.910 --> 00:09:32.480
with the court
and the Biluo Palace's support,

00:09:32.480 --> 00:09:35.080
the entire Sword Alliance's morale
has soared.

00:09:35.080 --> 00:09:36.010
I think we should

00:09:36.200 --> 00:09:37.790
take advantage while people are willing

00:09:37.790 --> 00:09:40.080
to fully eliminate
all Fengliu Shop strongholds.

00:09:40.080 --> 00:09:41.480
I've already sent Chunji

00:09:41.480 --> 00:09:43.210
to lead a reconnaissance team.

00:09:43.870 --> 00:09:44.670
Master Cheng,

00:09:44.910 --> 00:09:46.110
what's your opinion?

00:09:46.480 --> 00:09:49.140
Eliminating evil completely
is indeed my wish.

00:09:51.370 --> 00:09:52.410
But...

00:09:53.680 --> 00:09:55.280
Do we have to meet here?

00:09:55.390 --> 00:09:56.510
It's so dark here,

00:09:56.510 --> 00:09:57.600
making us look like

00:09:57.600 --> 00:09:59.660
we're plotting something sinister.

00:10:01.650 --> 00:10:03.850
Master Puzhu dislikes crowded places.

00:10:04.030 --> 00:10:05.360
The deeper one is in darkness,

00:10:05.360 --> 00:10:07.200
the more one craves for light.

00:10:09.740 --> 00:10:10.830
With enemies at our doorstep,

00:10:10.830 --> 00:10:12.100
if the Sword Alliance
needs anything in the future,

00:10:12.100 --> 00:10:13.760
just send someone to inform me.

00:10:13.760 --> 00:10:15.380
I will go to Wanhua Hall

00:10:15.600 --> 00:10:16.840
to discuss matters with you.

00:10:16.840 --> 00:10:17.390
Great.

00:10:18.000 --> 00:10:18.930
I never expected

00:10:19.020 --> 00:10:20.690
Master Puzhu to be

00:10:21.120 --> 00:10:23.180
someone who knows how to be flexible.

00:10:32.000 --> 00:10:33.490
To raid Fengliu Shop's strongholds,

00:10:33.490 --> 00:10:34.620
I'll lead by example

00:10:35.190 --> 00:10:36.250
and go ahead first.

00:10:37.670 --> 00:10:38.750
Perfect.

00:10:39.390 --> 00:10:40.550
Deputy Lord Yu

00:10:40.550 --> 00:10:42.870
has just arrived at the Sword Alliance
with his people.

00:10:42.870 --> 00:10:44.870
I'll go with you to see him.

00:10:46.480 --> 00:10:47.360
Master Puzhu,

00:10:47.910 --> 00:10:49.450
is it really so unbearable for you

00:10:49.450 --> 00:10:50.790
to work alongside me?

00:10:51.960 --> 00:10:52.910
I've heard

00:10:53.030 --> 00:10:54.920
that the disciples
of the Tianjing Pavilion

00:10:54.920 --> 00:10:57.200
must practice meditation and tolerance.

00:10:57.200 --> 00:10:57.670
How is it

00:10:57.910 --> 00:11:00.040
that you don't need to practice these?

00:11:05.320 --> 00:11:06.520
Farewell. Farewell.

00:11:07.570 --> 00:11:09.570
I wish you good luck on your journey.

00:11:17.060 --> 00:11:18.020
If Master Cheng

00:11:18.270 --> 00:11:19.600
also wants to talk about

00:11:19.950 --> 00:11:21.190
approval

00:11:21.410 --> 00:11:22.410
or other clichés,

00:11:22.630 --> 00:11:23.750
I already know it.

00:11:25.480 --> 00:11:27.000
Perhaps you do have the skills

00:11:27.000 --> 00:11:28.870
to fight against the Fengliu Shop.

00:11:28.870 --> 00:11:30.390
But with your personality,

00:11:30.390 --> 00:11:31.790
you can't inherit
the Seven‑String True Tune

00:11:31.790 --> 00:11:32.790
of Fang Zhou.

00:11:38.240 --> 00:11:39.080
Fang Zhou

00:11:40.350 --> 00:11:41.610
was a man of integrity,

00:11:43.090 --> 00:11:44.120
but in the end,

00:11:46.320 --> 00:11:48.240
apart from people's respect,

00:11:49.280 --> 00:11:50.410
what else did he get?

00:11:51.320 --> 00:11:53.120
Asking such a question shows

00:11:53.790 --> 00:11:56.250
you don't understand
Fang Zhou well enough.

00:11:56.870 --> 00:11:58.400
I don't want to be Fang Zhou.

00:11:58.890 --> 00:12:00.290
You can't be him either.

00:12:12.000 --> 00:12:14.240
You're suspected of being Yique Yinyang.

00:12:14.240 --> 00:12:15.790
Though after the battle at Biluo Palace,

00:12:15.790 --> 00:12:17.690
this suspicion was temporarily dispelled,

00:12:17.690 --> 00:12:19.620
but with your methods and actions,

00:12:19.790 --> 00:12:21.030
no one can guarantee

00:12:21.600 --> 00:12:22.750
that you won't become the next

00:12:22.750 --> 00:12:23.750
Yique Yinyang.

00:12:24.720 --> 00:12:26.080
You are a threat

00:12:26.510 --> 00:12:27.770
to the Sword Alliance.

00:12:28.670 --> 00:12:29.270
Tang Lici.

00:12:32.360 --> 00:12:33.560
I'll be watching you.

00:12:35.910 --> 00:12:36.970
You asked me before

00:12:37.390 --> 00:12:39.000
if I've ever killed the wrong person
with my sword.

00:12:39.000 --> 00:12:39.860
Perhaps I have,

00:12:40.720 --> 00:12:41.920
but I have no regrets.

00:12:42.240 --> 00:12:43.370
For all my mistakes,

00:12:43.910 --> 00:12:45.390
I will atone in hell.

00:12:51.210 --> 00:12:52.410
Why are you laughing?

00:12:56.470 --> 00:12:57.630
Master Cheng, your words

00:12:57.630 --> 00:12:58.870
sound so resolute.

00:12:59.390 --> 00:12:59.870
Have you

00:12:59.870 --> 00:13:01.930
moved yourself with your own speech?

00:13:02.230 --> 00:13:02.920
However,

00:13:03.630 --> 00:13:05.560
your desire to atone is one-sided.

00:13:06.120 --> 00:13:07.250
Have you considered

00:13:07.630 --> 00:13:09.160
whether those souls in hell

00:13:09.750 --> 00:13:10.870
are willing to give you

00:13:10.870 --> 00:13:12.270
a chance for redemption?

00:13:45.390 --> 00:13:46.360
Mr. Tang.

00:13:49.000 --> 00:13:51.330
Master Shao, you haven't slept all night.

00:13:51.720 --> 00:13:53.690
The turmoil in the jianghu hasn't settled,

00:13:53.690 --> 00:13:55.620
making it impossible to rest easy.

00:13:59.600 --> 00:14:00.800
Forgive my boldness,

00:14:00.890 --> 00:14:03.490
are you and the owner of the Fengliu Shop
Liu Yan

00:14:04.550 --> 00:14:06.210
disciples of the same master?

00:14:08.050 --> 00:14:09.780
Chief Fang Zhou of Zhoudi Tower

00:14:10.480 --> 00:14:11.720
was our senior.

00:14:13.720 --> 00:14:15.150
Chief Fang Zhou of Zhoudi Tower

00:14:15.150 --> 00:14:16.410
was a man of principle.

00:14:16.420 --> 00:14:18.570
My master Jiangnan Feng and he

00:14:19.030 --> 00:14:21.010
once fought fiercely at Tiandu Peak,

00:14:21.010 --> 00:14:23.510
together resisting
Yique Yinyang's rebellion.

00:14:23.510 --> 00:14:25.970
Mr. Tang,
since you've inherited his legacy

00:14:26.200 --> 00:14:27.660
and are willing to join us,

00:14:28.160 --> 00:14:30.760
you must also have the desire
to help the world.

00:14:31.000 --> 00:14:32.120
But my purpose

00:14:32.120 --> 00:14:34.120
has never been peace in the jianghu.

00:14:34.190 --> 00:14:35.720
That's not contradictory.

00:14:36.390 --> 00:14:37.790
Didn't you once tell

00:14:37.790 --> 00:14:39.080
Master Puzhu

00:14:39.550 --> 00:14:41.790
that even those with different paths
can work together?

00:14:41.790 --> 00:14:43.720
As long as our current goals align,

00:14:43.790 --> 00:14:45.480
why not journey together for a while?

00:14:45.480 --> 00:14:47.150
Rest assured,
since we're traveling together,

00:14:47.150 --> 00:14:48.120
I will handle

00:14:48.180 --> 00:14:50.310
all Sword Alliance matters properly.

00:14:50.630 --> 00:14:51.240
However,

00:14:51.670 --> 00:14:53.150
my methods in the future

00:14:53.270 --> 00:14:55.550
may be even more unacceptable
to ordinary people.

00:14:55.550 --> 00:14:57.080
You

00:14:57.480 --> 00:14:59.940
might not have peace and quiet
for some time.

00:15:02.680 --> 00:15:03.280
Everyone,

00:15:03.550 --> 00:15:04.630
don't be hasty!

00:15:04.870 --> 00:15:06.320
Let's talk things through slowly!

00:15:06.320 --> 00:15:06.960
Tang Lici!

00:15:11.180 --> 00:15:12.280
Take it easy. Calm down.

00:15:12.280 --> 00:15:13.060
Let's talk this through.

00:15:13.060 --> 00:15:13.970
Sword Masters.

00:15:14.840 --> 00:15:15.510
What's the matter?

00:15:15.510 --> 00:15:16.800
You've made a mistake in this decree.

00:15:16.800 --> 00:15:18.190
I'm in charge of the Service Hall,

00:15:18.190 --> 00:15:19.720
not the Investigation Hall.

00:15:19.720 --> 00:15:20.450
And mine too.

00:15:20.670 --> 00:15:22.170
If you transfer me elsewhere,

00:15:22.170 --> 00:15:25.230
what will happen to my cases
at the Investigation Hall?

00:15:26.420 --> 00:15:27.950
Whatever you have received

00:15:28.540 --> 00:15:30.000
is what you should follow.

00:15:31.150 --> 00:15:32.510
You don't understand the Sword Alliance,

00:15:32.510 --> 00:15:34.000
so please stop messing things up.

00:15:34.000 --> 00:15:34.910
If you turn

00:15:34.910 --> 00:15:35.750
the Sword Alliance into chaos

00:15:35.750 --> 00:15:36.790
and then just walk away,

00:15:36.790 --> 00:15:38.250
what are we supposed to do?

00:15:40.240 --> 00:15:41.080
Mr. Tang,

00:15:41.510 --> 00:15:42.640
even though you were

00:15:42.750 --> 00:15:45.120
invited by
our Ancestor's divine revelation,

00:15:45.120 --> 00:15:46.320
you still

00:15:46.320 --> 00:15:47.520
can't be so arbitrary

00:15:47.520 --> 00:15:48.790
and autocratic.

00:15:51.120 --> 00:15:51.920
Master Jiang,

00:15:52.080 --> 00:15:53.870
during your supervision of disciples,

00:15:53.870 --> 00:15:55.440
their efficiency was poor,

