Well,

00:29:39.270 --> 00:29:40.810
there's nothing I can do about it.

00:29:40.810 --> 00:29:42.410
My parents gave me this name.

00:29:43.030 --> 00:29:44.590
It's my honor
to share the same pronunciation

00:29:44.590 --> 00:29:46.070
as Head Fang's name.

00:29:46.290 --> 00:29:48.000
Surely Head Fang was generous enough

00:29:48.000 --> 00:29:49.750
to tolerate someone like me.

00:29:50.000 --> 00:29:50.550
Besides,

00:29:50.880 --> 00:29:52.200
Head Fang's "Zhou" means

00:29:52.200 --> 00:29:54.350
encompassing the world,

00:29:54.350 --> 00:29:55.460
while my "Zhou" is just

00:29:55.460 --> 00:29:57.110
a lonely boat drifting

00:29:57.110 --> 00:29:58.790
in this vast universe.

00:30:01.400 --> 00:30:02.440
Even so,

00:30:03.430 --> 00:30:04.630
I kindly advise you

00:30:04.990 --> 00:30:06.360
if you meet Mr. Tang,

00:30:07.830 --> 00:30:08.560
you'd better

00:30:09.440 --> 00:30:10.830
not mention your name.

00:30:11.960 --> 00:30:12.550
Why?

00:30:13.720 --> 00:30:15.850
Just because my name is also Fang Zhou?

00:30:16.160 --> 00:30:17.920
There are countless people
with the same name.

00:30:17.920 --> 00:30:19.070
Besides me, there must be

00:30:19.070 --> 00:30:20.750
thousands of other Fang Zhous.

00:30:20.750 --> 00:30:21.720
Are you saying

00:30:21.720 --> 00:30:23.850
Mr. Tang can't stand to see any of them?

00:30:24.070 --> 00:30:26.600
Is he really that arbitrary
and domineering?

00:30:26.790 --> 00:30:27.510
Yeah.

00:30:27.790 --> 00:30:29.160
That's too domineering.

00:30:29.160 --> 00:30:30.310
That's so unreasonable.

00:30:30.310 --> 00:30:32.160
How is Mr. Tang being arbitrary
and domineering?

00:30:32.160 --> 00:30:32.830
You don't know him,

00:30:32.830 --> 00:30:34.230
so don't speak nonsense.

00:30:39.120 --> 00:30:40.690
This is indeed my fault.

00:30:41.070 --> 00:30:42.960
I apologize to you, Miss.

00:30:43.720 --> 00:30:44.780
Alright, alright.

00:30:45.240 --> 00:30:47.110
We don't stand on ceremony
at the Sword Alliance.

00:30:47.110 --> 00:30:49.110
Go get your disciple uniform first.

00:30:49.210 --> 00:30:50.400
Thank you very much, Miss.

00:30:50.400 --> 00:30:52.030
Don't go! Read my fortune!

00:30:52.510 --> 00:30:53.750
Tell my fortune!

00:30:53.750 --> 00:30:55.480
Don't rush. Don't rush.

00:30:55.750 --> 00:30:56.480
One at a time.

00:31:00.160 --> 00:31:00.590
Good.

00:31:02.070 --> 00:31:02.790
Obviously,

00:31:02.790 --> 00:31:04.850
this is a diagram of human meridians.

00:31:05.020 --> 00:31:05.740
So today,

00:31:06.160 --> 00:31:07.890
I'll be explaining to everyone

00:31:08.270 --> 00:31:09.590
how the modified version

00:31:09.590 --> 00:31:10.640
of the Blood Ghost Pill
from the Fengliu Shop

00:31:10.640 --> 00:31:12.300
causes harm to the human body.

00:31:12.900 --> 00:31:15.070
Of course,
my explanation might be insufficient.

00:31:15.070 --> 00:31:16.530
Shen will fill in the gaps.

00:31:17.030 --> 00:31:18.180
What's the difference

00:31:18.180 --> 00:31:19.590
between the current Blood Ghost Pill

00:31:19.590 --> 00:31:20.960
and the poison pill
spread by the Jile Sect

00:31:20.960 --> 00:31:22.220
from over a decade ago?

00:31:22.320 --> 00:31:25.070
The former is more potent,
and its toxicity is more concealed.

00:31:25.070 --> 00:31:26.920
The one who refined the poison pill
is not anyone else

00:31:26.920 --> 00:31:27.680
but the current Master

00:31:27.680 --> 00:31:29.000
of the Fengliu Shop, Liu Yan.

00:31:29.000 --> 00:31:29.960
Fine, fine.

00:31:30.490 --> 00:31:33.620
The underworld is giving a lesson
to the upright people.

00:31:33.980 --> 00:31:35.070
Indeed, when you live long enough,

00:31:35.070 --> 00:31:36.400
you'll see everything.

00:31:36.490 --> 00:31:37.590
Among these people,

00:31:37.590 --> 00:31:39.240
only Chi Yun and Shen Langhun

00:31:39.370 --> 00:31:40.830
fought against people

00:31:40.830 --> 00:31:41.960
who took the new Evil Pill.

00:31:41.960 --> 00:31:43.490
The poison pill he modified

00:31:43.790 --> 00:31:44.550
can make the user's power

00:31:44.550 --> 00:31:45.790
increase more than tenfold.

00:31:45.790 --> 00:31:46.880
You sneaky fox,

00:31:47.110 --> 00:31:48.970
always appearing out of nowhere.

00:31:49.790 --> 00:31:50.480
I heard

00:31:50.480 --> 00:31:52.200
a fortune teller
joined the Sword Alliance.

00:31:52.200 --> 00:31:54.000
Why don't you go see him?

00:31:54.790 --> 00:31:55.790
A fortune teller?

00:31:56.880 --> 00:31:58.720
I saw you and Shei

00:31:58.790 --> 00:32:00.790
whispering by the stream.

00:32:02.000 --> 00:32:04.110
I'm saying you should go see him too,

00:32:04.500 --> 00:32:05.640
to see if someone as ice-cold as you

00:32:05.640 --> 00:32:06.900
can turn into a softie.

00:32:13.030 --> 00:32:15.830
It's over. It's over.

00:32:16.480 --> 00:32:18.270
It's all over. It's all over.

00:32:21.240 --> 00:32:23.240
You'll soon face a bloody disaster.

00:32:23.400 --> 00:32:25.200
How can I avoid it?
Do you have any magic charms?

00:32:25.200 --> 00:32:26.000
Magic charms?

00:32:27.510 --> 00:32:28.310
Of course not.

00:32:29.140 --> 00:32:30.030
Just don't go outside,

00:32:30.030 --> 00:32:31.090
and you'll be fine.

00:32:31.520 --> 00:32:32.400
Thank you, Mr. Fang.

00:32:32.400 --> 00:32:33.530
Thank you, Mr. Fang.

00:32:34.830 --> 00:32:35.880
That won't work.

00:32:36.160 --> 00:32:37.310
We have to get up at dawn

00:32:37.310 --> 00:32:38.880
to practice sword formations.

00:32:38.880 --> 00:32:39.750
This was arranged

00:32:39.750 --> 00:32:40.880
by Mr. Tang.

00:32:40.880 --> 00:32:42.510
He makes you get up at dawn?

00:32:42.510 --> 00:32:43.640
-Yes.
-That's right.

00:32:43.640 --> 00:32:44.340
Yes.

00:32:44.360 --> 00:32:45.990
What is Mr. Tang thinking?

00:32:46.160 --> 00:32:47.740
What's on Mr. Tang's mind?

00:32:48.200 --> 00:32:49.200
How would ordinary disciples like us

00:32:49.200 --> 00:32:49.960
know?

00:32:50.440 --> 00:32:52.310
Could you decipher this for us?

00:32:52.810 --> 00:32:53.370
Yes.

00:32:53.400 --> 00:32:54.070
Please do us a favor.

00:32:54.070 --> 00:32:54.830
Please.

00:32:54.830 --> 00:32:55.680
Let me try.

00:32:55.880 --> 00:32:57.880
If you want to know what's on my mind,

00:32:59.080 --> 00:33:00.550
why don't you ask me directly?

00:33:00.550 --> 00:33:01.940
-Mr. Tang.
-Mr. Tang.

00:33:04.030 --> 00:33:05.230
You haven't paid yet.

00:33:12.580 --> 00:33:13.380
Interesting.

00:33:13.920 --> 00:33:14.510
Welcome.

00:33:15.350 --> 00:33:16.830
Would you like your future read

00:33:16.830 --> 00:33:18.430
or your lifespan predicted?

00:33:20.480 --> 00:33:22.940
My surname is Fang,
courtesy name Pingzhai,

00:33:23.110 --> 00:33:25.790
and nickname Carefree.

00:33:27.290 --> 00:33:30.100
So Mr. Carefree Fang,

00:33:32.160 --> 00:33:34.290
your profession is fortune-telling?

00:33:36.190 --> 00:33:37.320
Just a humble skill.

00:33:37.830 --> 00:33:39.000
It's not even one-tenth

00:33:39.000 --> 00:33:40.200
of what I've learned.

00:33:40.310 --> 00:33:40.910
By the way,

00:33:41.800 --> 00:33:43.730
let me formally introduce myself.

00:33:44.160 --> 00:33:46.310
My surname is Fang, given name Zhou,

00:33:48.270 --> 00:33:49.870
and courtesy name Pingzhai.

00:33:50.590 --> 00:33:51.720
Pleased to meet you.

00:33:54.400 --> 00:33:56.000
What did you say your name is?

00:33:56.240 --> 00:33:58.520
I am

00:33:59.200 --> 00:34:00.270
Fang Zhou.

00:34:10.960 --> 00:34:13.150
You don't stay in Fallen Shisan Tower.

00:34:14.510 --> 00:34:16.710
Why have you come to the Sword Alliance?

00:34:16.870 --> 00:34:19.389
You know,
the Sword Alliance is open to all.

00:34:19.940 --> 00:34:20.790
If you can come

00:34:21.190 --> 00:34:22.190
and Shen can come,

00:34:22.400 --> 00:34:23.760
why can't I come?

00:34:24.280 --> 00:34:26.630
I also wish to follow the righteous path.

00:34:29.190 --> 00:34:30.480
What do you want?

00:34:36.800 --> 00:34:37.710
Mr. Tang,

00:34:38.690 --> 00:34:40.880
you have a supreme martial art technique

00:34:40.880 --> 00:34:42.880
called the Rebirth Scroll.

00:34:45.070 --> 00:34:47.070
Endless Secrets of Heaven and Earth,

00:34:47.070 --> 00:34:49.280
Liuli Rebirth Scroll.

00:34:57.480 --> 00:34:59.080
You've given yourself away.

00:35:01.150 --> 00:35:02.320
Chief Fang.

00:35:08.070 --> 00:35:09.320
Fallen Shisan Tower.

00:35:09.960 --> 00:35:12.840
Chief Fang of Dieban Chonghua.

00:35:14.280 --> 00:35:16.540
What do you want with the Rebirth Scroll?

00:35:17.290 --> 00:35:19.030
You claim to join the righteous path,

00:35:19.030 --> 00:35:19.880
yet you're here for

00:35:19.880 --> 00:35:22.120
Yique Yinyang's martial arts technique.

00:35:22.120 --> 00:35:23.560
I've been exposed.

00:35:24.100 --> 00:35:25.150
Why don't you just play along with me

00:35:25.150 --> 00:35:25.840
for a while?

00:35:27.520 --> 00:35:28.780
But come to think of it,

00:35:29.330 --> 00:35:31.760
you possess
Yique Yinyang's martial arts technique,

00:35:31.760 --> 00:35:32.760
and you've become

00:35:32.760 --> 00:35:34.890
a Guest of Honor of the Sword Alliance.

00:35:35.480 --> 00:35:36.540
Is there a problem?

00:35:37.700 --> 00:35:38.300
Forget it.

00:35:39.200 --> 00:35:42.320
Since the Guest of Honor
of the Sword Alliance can't offer it,

00:35:42.320 --> 00:35:43.800
I'd like to see

00:35:44.230 --> 00:35:47.320
whether Master Liu
from the Fengliu Shop will give it to me.

00:35:47.320 --> 00:35:48.380
Stay away from him.

00:35:50.190 --> 00:35:51.150
Otherwise,

00:35:53.960 --> 00:35:54.760
I'll make sure

00:35:55.280 --> 00:35:57.340
you'll get it but won't live to use it.

00:35:59.880 --> 00:36:02.360
Mr. Tang, I've read your fortune.

00:36:02.850 --> 00:36:04.450
The results are surprising.

00:36:08.010 --> 00:36:11.340
You're not a human of this world

00:36:12.320 --> 00:36:14.480
but a fox demon.

00:36:20.580 --> 00:36:22.090
Then you should also know

00:36:23.670 --> 00:36:25.030
that fox demons excel at

00:36:25.990 --> 00:36:27.200
gutting humans

00:36:28.550 --> 00:36:30.150
and digging out their hearts

00:36:30.600 --> 00:36:31.930
to examine them closely

00:36:32.710 --> 00:36:34.910
to see if they're loyal or treacherous.

00:36:44.630 --> 00:36:45.690
Why is it you again?

00:36:46.430 --> 00:36:47.230
We hired you

00:36:47.230 --> 00:36:48.630
not to deceive others.

00:36:49.630 --> 00:36:50.280
Mr. Tang,

00:36:50.510 --> 00:36:51.000
did he

00:36:51.530 --> 00:36:53.050
tell you any nonsense?

00:36:53.510 --> 00:36:54.190
Ms. Zhong,

00:36:54.670 --> 00:36:55.600
long time no see.

00:36:56.280 --> 00:36:57.210
Long time no see.

00:36:57.510 --> 00:36:58.570
Don't worry, Miss.

00:36:59.000 --> 00:36:59.880
Mr. Tang

00:36:59.980 --> 00:37:01.950
has found me a good job.

00:37:02.880 --> 00:37:04.880
I won't be fortune-telling anymore.

00:37:04.880 --> 00:37:05.680
That's right.

00:37:06.490 --> 00:37:08.380
A job very suitable for Mr. Fang.

00:37:10.400 --> 00:37:12.800
During your time working
at the Service Hall,

00:37:12.800 --> 00:37:13.760
I hope you

00:37:13.760 --> 00:37:15.030
can think carefully

00:37:15.890 --> 00:37:17.490
whether you want to be honest

00:37:17.520 --> 00:37:18.600
with me or not.

00:37:20.960 --> 00:37:22.190
You want me to do odd jobs?

00:37:22.190 --> 00:37:23.190
Do them properly.

00:37:34.710 --> 00:37:36.440
When did you return, Ms. Zhong?

00:37:38.760 --> 00:37:39.690
About 2 days ago.

00:37:40.070 --> 00:37:41.710
Master said you were busy.

00:37:41.800 --> 00:37:43.920
If I hadn't seen you
while passing by just now,

00:37:43.920 --> 00:37:45.880
I wouldn't have come to bother you again.

00:37:45.880 --> 00:37:47.080
Even if we hadn't met,

00:37:47.810 --> 00:37:49.810
I would come looking for you anyway.

00:38:04.150 --> 00:38:04.960
I heard

00:38:06.000 --> 00:38:07.530
that you lost your position

00:38:07.590 --> 00:38:10.520
as Branch Chief
of the Shanfeng Branch because of me.

00:38:12.440 --> 00:38:13.800
I lost my position

00:38:14.480 --> 00:38:16.280
because someone else wanted it.

00:38:17.110 --> 00:38:18.000
Mr. Tang, you don't need

00:38:18.000 --> 00:38:19.930
to take everything upon yourself.

00:38:20.230 --> 00:38:20.960
I just

00:38:21.510 --> 00:38:22.800
feel it's unfair.

00:38:25.590 --> 00:38:27.790
There's no such thing as fair or unfair.

00:38:27.800 --> 00:38:28.670
It has always been about

00:38:28.670 --> 00:38:30.530
whether others choose you or not.

00:38:31.030 --> 00:38:31.630
I think

00:38:32.190 --> 00:38:33.150
Master Shao must

00:38:33.150 --> 00:38:34.680
have his own difficulties.

00:38:37.360 --> 00:38:37.960
Ms. Zhong.

00:38:39.920 --> 00:38:41.180
Come with me to a place.

00:38:43.590 --> 00:38:44.120
Let's go.

00:38:49.920 --> 00:38:50.920
The food is ready.

00:38:51.920 --> 00:38:53.050
And the wine is here.

00:38:53.400 --> 00:38:55.190
Did you twist your ankle, Miss Shei?

00:38:55.190 --> 00:38:55.920
Take it easy.

00:38:56.630 --> 00:38:57.320
Ms. Zhong.

00:39:01.730 --> 00:39:02.230
Zhong.

00:39:02.400 --> 00:39:03.030
Ms. Zhong.

00:39:08.510 --> 00:39:09.510
Everyone's here.

00:39:12.280 --> 00:39:13.400
Why are you so late?

00:39:13.840 --> 00:39:15.590
We've been waiting for you
for a long time.

00:39:15.590 --> 00:39:17.590
Shen and I finished our lessons ages ago.

00:39:17.590 --> 00:39:19.430
Those Sword Masters
kept asking us questions.

00:39:19.430 --> 00:39:20.270
They asked me.

00:39:20.290 --> 00:39:22.150
You couldn't explain it clearly.

00:39:24.030 --> 00:39:24.630
Ms. Zhong,

00:39:25.050 --> 00:39:25.980
please sit down.

00:39:26.340 --> 00:39:27.340
Come, have a seat.

00:39:36.280 --> 00:39:37.050
Ms. Zhong, you stood up for justice,

00:39:37.050 --> 00:39:37.670
♪ Did you ever wonder then ♪

00:39:37.670 --> 00:39:39.270
yet you were punished for it.

00:39:39.360 --> 00:39:39.920
I

00:39:40.630 --> 00:39:42.280
feel it's completely unfair for you.

00:39:42.280 --> 00:39:42.590
♪ As night quietly fell, to ask the moon ♪

00:39:42.590 --> 00:39:43.520
But don't worry.

00:39:44.000 --> 00:39:45.550
When we battle against the Fengliu Shop,

00:39:45.550 --> 00:39:46.730
Yanmen Sect will lead the charge,

00:39:46.730 --> 00:39:47.060
and you'll definitely have a chance
to prove yourself.

00:39:47.060 --> 00:39:48.990
♪ When the next dawn comes ♪

00:39:48.990 --> 00:39:50.190
That's right, Zhong.

00:39:50.190 --> 00:39:50.920
Take it easy.

00:39:51.490 --> 00:39:52.730
I believe you can do it.

00:39:52.730 --> 00:39:55.480
♪ Will we too be forgotten? ♪

00:39:55.480 --> 00:39:56.110
Everyone

00:39:56.760 --> 00:39:57.560
will help you return
to the Shanfeng Branch.

00:39:57.560 --> 00:40:01.810
♪ The sunlight falls upon you ♪

00:40:01.840 --> 00:40:02.160
Then

00:40:02.160 --> 00:40:03.590
♪ Just like when you asked me back then ♪

00:40:03.590 --> 00:40:04.390
thank you all.

00:40:06.360 --> 00:40:07.760
Thank you, Master Jiang.

00:40:07.760 --> 00:40:09.840
♪ How do we hide certain answers ♪

00:40:09.840 --> 00:40:10.440
Thank you,

00:40:11.590 --> 00:40:12.280
Mr. Tang.

00:40:12.510 --> 00:40:14.360
♪ Those burning moments with you? ♪

00:40:14.360 --> 00:40:14.960
Ms. Zhong,

00:40:15.190 --> 00:40:16.250
no need for thanks.

00:40:16.510 --> 00:40:17.240
Fengliu Shop

00:40:17.550 --> 00:40:17.970
tricked my son into taking the Evil Pill.

00:40:17.970 --> 00:40:20.000
♪ The sunlight falls upon you ♪

00:40:20.000 --> 00:40:21.460
If it weren't for Ms. Zhong

00:40:21.550 --> 00:40:22.550
and everyone else

00:40:22.550 --> 00:40:22.670
helping me expose the traitor,

00:40:22.670 --> 00:40:25.150
♪ Just like when you asked me back then ♪

00:40:25.150 --> 00:40:26.880
Yanmen Sect would be in danger.

00:40:27.360 --> 00:40:28.260
Both officially and personally,

00:40:28.260 --> 00:40:28.480
♪ How do we hide certain answers ♪

00:40:28.480 --> 00:40:29.510
I should help you.

00:40:29.980 --> 00:40:32.020
Let's not talk about this now.

00:40:32.690 --> 00:40:32.960
♪ Those burning moments with you? ♪

00:40:32.960 --> 00:40:35.160
Let's enjoy this brief moment of peace.

00:40:35.230 --> 00:40:36.960
What wine did you bring, Jiang?

00:40:37.630 --> 00:40:39.630
This is the finest wine from Yanmen.

00:40:40.070 --> 00:40:41.230
Frosty Leaves' Red.

00:40:41.590 --> 00:40:43.650
A Yanmen specialty, excellent wine.

00:40:43.890 --> 00:40:45.760
Paired with Shei's delicious dishes,

00:40:45.760 --> 00:40:48.030
there is wine and food. Let me try first.

00:40:48.030 --> 00:40:48.760
Chi,

00:40:49.370 --> 00:40:51.170
don't start eating by yourself.

00:40:51.880 --> 00:40:52.360
I...

00:40:53.000 --> 00:40:53.800
It's alright.

00:40:54.040 --> 00:40:56.330
Today is a family gathering;
no need for formalities.

00:40:56.330 --> 00:40:57.990
Everyone, let's have a toast.

00:40:58.380 --> 00:41:02.670
♪ The northern wind hums by my ear ♪

00:41:02.670 --> 00:41:03.130
Cheers.

00:41:03.990 --> 00:41:08.180
♪ Stirring waves between your brows ♪

00:41:08.320 --> 00:41:13.960
♪ The flowers scatter in June ♪

00:41:14.160 --> 00:41:18.240
♪ I'd rather jump into your soil ♪

00:41:19.230 --> 00:41:19.880
Ms. Zhong.

00:41:21.320 --> 00:41:22.250
Are you unhappy?

00:41:23.630 --> 00:41:24.190
No.

00:41:25.030 --> 00:41:26.000
I just feel

00:41:27.070 --> 00:41:28.330
that it feels like ages

00:41:28.840 --> 00:41:30.320
since I last saw everyone.

00:41:31.070 --> 00:41:33.150
The last time we went to Sword King City

00:41:33.150 --> 00:41:35.480
seems like it happened in a previous life.

00:41:38.140 --> 00:41:39.670
I'd like to toast everyone.

00:41:40.550 --> 00:41:41.830
No matter how much time passes,

00:41:41.830 --> 00:41:43.690
we should always drink together.

00:41:43.760 --> 00:41:45.290
You always know what to say.

00:42:11.330 --> 00:42:13.530
You seem very happy tonight, Ms. Zhong.

00:42:14.120 --> 00:42:15.180
Why is it you again?

00:42:16.590 --> 00:42:17.710
Do you need something?

00:42:17.710 --> 00:42:18.760
I asked you first.

00:42:19.180 --> 00:42:20.840
So you should answer me first.

00:42:21.030 --> 00:42:22.430
Of course I'm happy.

00:42:23.360 --> 00:42:23.960
Your turn.

00:42:24.220 --> 00:42:25.440
I don't have anything specific.

00:42:25.440 --> 00:42:25.880
Why?

00:42:26.360 --> 00:42:28.490
Can't I chat with you without a reason?

00:42:31.310 --> 00:42:32.790
You're so strange.

00:42:33.630 --> 00:42:34.760
If you came to the Sword Alliance

00:42:34.760 --> 00:42:36.090
with other intentions,

00:42:36.250 --> 00:42:37.250
I suggest

00:42:38.140 --> 00:42:39.420
you leave now.

00:42:40.510 --> 00:42:41.970
You're quite perceptive.

00:42:42.710 --> 00:42:43.230
Fine.

00:42:43.590 --> 00:42:44.390
I'll tell you.

00:42:44.990 --> 00:42:46.480
I came to the Sword Alliance

00:42:46.480 --> 00:42:47.960
to see

00:42:48.150 --> 00:42:50.110
the true face of the fox demon.

00:42:51.940 --> 00:42:52.590
Why?

00:42:53.260 --> 00:42:53.820
Why?

00:42:55.030 --> 00:42:55.760
Because...

00:42:56.690 --> 00:42:59.290
Mr. Tang is indeed detestable and hateful,

00:42:59.840 --> 00:43:00.960
but I must admit

00:43:01.360 --> 00:43:04.000
that he does have a captivating charm.

00:43:04.550 --> 00:43:06.150
It makes one unable to resist

00:43:06.510 --> 00:43:08.000
falling deeply for him.

00:43:11.670 --> 00:43:13.280
You dare to provoke Mr. Tang?

00:43:14.280 --> 00:43:16.510
Aren't you afraid
that you'll bring disaster upon yourself?

00:43:16.510 --> 00:43:18.880
It's the danger that makes it attractive.

00:43:19.230 --> 00:43:19.880
You

00:43:19.880 --> 00:43:22.210
understand this feeling best, don't you?

00:43:24.150 --> 00:43:26.240
What are you talking about?

00:43:27.670 --> 00:43:29.280
What I want to say is,

00:43:29.740 --> 00:43:30.960
to get his attention,

00:43:31.520 --> 00:43:33.520
you can't follow the ordinary path.

00:43:34.630 --> 00:43:36.760
You need to be the most special person.

00:43:37.280 --> 00:43:38.920
Don't let yourself need him;

00:43:39.290 --> 00:43:41.690
make him need you instead.

00:43:43.380 --> 00:43:45.300
What's between Mr. Tang and me

00:43:45.960 --> 00:43:47.480
is none of your business.

00:43:49.430 --> 00:43:50.510
To be honest,

00:43:50.710 --> 00:43:52.240
I've read your fortune too.

00:43:53.200 --> 00:43:55.840
Your destiny shows weak family bonds

00:43:56.110 --> 00:43:57.510
and no power or wealth.

00:43:58.030 --> 00:43:59.630
What others are born with,

00:43:59.800 --> 00:44:01.230
you must fight desperately to obtain—

00:44:01.230 --> 00:44:03.630
only then might you stand a slim chance
of getting it.

00:44:03.630 --> 00:44:05.490
If you miss just one opportunity,

00:44:06.840 --> 00:44:08.320
you'll lose everything.

00:44:14.070 --> 00:44:15.440
Mr. Fang, do you think

00:44:15.730 --> 00:44:17.260
I would believe your words?

00:44:17.580 --> 00:44:19.170
It doesn't matter if you don't.

00:44:19.170 --> 00:44:20.230
But if I were you,

00:44:20.230 --> 00:44:21.440
with such a fate,

00:44:21.540 --> 00:44:22.480
I would contentedly

00:44:22.480 --> 00:44:23.880
be an ordinary disciple

00:44:24.590 --> 00:44:26.320
and marry a simple, honest man.

00:44:27.110 --> 00:44:28.370
Why struggle for more?

00:44:29.590 --> 00:44:31.320
What if I insist on struggling?

00:44:35.480 --> 00:44:36.960
Then I can help you.

00:44:43.460 --> 00:44:44.320
I don't need it.

00:44:48.820 --> 00:44:49.920
Think carefully,

00:44:50.300 --> 00:44:51.170
Ms. Zhong.

00:45:20.240 --> 00:45:21.770
A letter from Shisan Tower.

00:45:22.340 --> 00:45:24.650
The Peach of Three Hues in Pink Attire.

00:45:26.000 --> 00:45:27.190
She is Xifang Tao.

00:45:48.490 --> 00:45:50.350
Hand it to Godfather personally.

00:45:51.160 --> 00:45:52.370
Bring back his reply.

00:45:54.690 --> 00:45:57.020
Aren't you going
to ask what this is about?

00:45:58.220 --> 00:46:00.080
I don't have Chi Yun's curiosity.

00:46:00.630 --> 00:46:01.630
The more you know,

00:46:02.030 --> 00:46:03.090
the sooner you die.

00:46:13.370 --> 00:46:14.210
Sometimes,

00:46:15.100 --> 00:46:16.320
the more you know,

00:46:16.880 --> 00:46:18.280
the better your chances.

00:46:19.280 --> 00:46:20.320
Fang Pingzhai,

00:46:20.840 --> 00:46:22.000
your true identity

00:46:22.000 --> 00:46:23.480
is about to be revealed.